Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message

TNC message processing interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Combined<T>
    Generic helper to enable arbitrary message related objects to be stacked together via add and remove operations.
    Data
    Marker to characterize an object as a message or message component for TNC communication.
    Reader<T extends Data,S>
    Generic base for a reader, that reads data from a source and parses it to a Java object.
    ResultContainer<T extends Data>
    Generic base for a helper object to pass on a transmission result such as a message or batch and minor validation errors after parsing for further processing.
    TcgProtocolBindingIdentifier
    Extensible enumeration for protocol identifiers.
    TransmissionObjectBuilder<T>
    Generic builder base to build a transmission object such as batch, message or attribute.
    Writer<T extends Data,S>
    Generic base for a writer, that accepts a message object and serializes it to the given destination.
